{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "cortexcc-sim-canales-2026",
    "name": "CortexCC — Simulación de canales",
    "description": "Colección para simular mensajes entrantes y direccionamiento desde Postman.\n\n**Requisitos locales**\n- Backend en `http://localhost:3030`\n- Tenant `local` registrado en Master\n- `INTEGRATION_API_KEY` en backend `.env` (variable `integrationApiKey`)\n\n**IDs de canal (seed)**\n- WhatsApp: `seed-channel-WHATSAPP`\n- Webchat: `seed-channel-WEBCHAT`\n- Email: `seed-channel-EMAIL`\n- Voz: `seed-channel-VOICE`\n\n**WhatsApp webhook**\nEl canal debe tener en Configuración → Canales el `provider` que coincida con el payload (360dialog, twilio o ultramsg). Con config vacía `{}` el webhook fallará al procesar.\n\n**Webchat**\nNo tiene webhook HTTP; usa *Integraciones → Escalate* o *Crear conversación manual*.\n\n**Orden sugerido**\n1. Health + Login\n2. Webhook WhatsApp o Integración Escalate\n3. Listar conversaciones / Disparar routing",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3030/api" },
    { "key": "tenantKey", "value": "local" },
    { "key": "integrationApiKey", "value": "dev-integration-api-key-change-me" },
    { "key": "adminEmail", "value": "admin@cortex.local" },
    { "key": "adminPassword", "value": "demo1234" },
    { "key": "accessToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "whatsappChannelId", "value": "seed-channel-WHATSAPP" },
    { "key": "webchatChannelId", "value": "seed-channel-WEBCHAT" },
    { "key": "emailChannelId", "value": "seed-channel-EMAIL" },
    { "key": "voiceChannelId", "value": "seed-channel-VOICE" },
    { "key": "lastConversationId", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "01 — Setup y auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health (sin tenant)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/health"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Resolver tenant por host",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/tenants/resolve?host=localhost",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["tenants", "resolve"],
              "query": [{ "key": "host", "value": "localhost" }]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login admin (guarda token)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (data.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', data.token);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('accessToken', data.token);",
                  "  }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Tenant-Key", "value": "{{tenantKey}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{adminEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{adminPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar canales (settings)",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{accessToken}}", "type": "string" }]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "X-Tenant-Key", "value": "{{tenantKey}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/settings/channels"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Integraciones — status",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "X-Tenant-Key", "value": "{{tenantKey}}" },
              { "key": "x-api-key", "value": "{{integrationApiKey}}" }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/integrations/status"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "02 — WhatsApp webhooks",
      "description": "POST /webhooks/:tenantKey/whatsapp/:channelId\nNo requiere Authorization. El tenant va en la URL.\nRespuesta inmediata 202; el procesamiento es asíncrono.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "360dialog / Meta — texto entrante",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const id = 'wamid.' + Date.now();",
                  "pm.variables.set('waMsgId', id);",
                  "pm.variables.set('waFrom', '593991234567');"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"object\": \"whatsapp_business_account\",\n  \"entry\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"WABA_ID\",\n      \"changes\": [\n        {\n          \"value\": {\n            \"messaging_product\": \"whatsapp\",\n            \"metadata\": {\n              \"display_phone_number\": \"15550001111\",\n              \"phone_number_id\": \"PHONE_NUMBER_ID\"\n            },\n            \"contacts\": [\n              {\n                \"profile\": { \"name\": \"Cliente Postman\" },\n                \"wa_id\": \"{{waFrom}}\"\n              }\n            ],\n            \"messages\": [\n              {\n                \"from\": \"{{waFrom}}\",\n                \"id\": \"{{waMsgId}}\",\n                \"timestamp\": \"{{$timestamp}}\",\n                \"type\": \"text\",\n                \"text\": { \"body\": \"Hola, mensaje de prueba desde Postman (360dialog)\" }\n              }\n            ]\n          },\n          \"field\": \"messages\"\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/webhooks/{{tenantKey}}/whatsapp/{{whatsappChannelId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Twilio — texto entrante (form)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.variables.set('twilioSid', 'SM' + Date.now());"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "urlencoded",
              "urlencoded": [
                { "key": "MessageSid", "value": "{{twilioSid}}" },
                { "key": "From", "value": "whatsapp:+593991234567" },
                { "key": "To", "value": "whatsapp:+15550001111" },
                { "key": "Body", "value": "Hola desde Postman vía Twilio" },
                { "key": "ProfileName", "value": "Cliente Twilio" },
                { "key": "NumMedia", "value": "0" }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/webhooks/{{tenantKey}}/whatsapp/{{whatsappChannelId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "UltraMsg — texto entrante",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.variables.set('ultraMsgId', 'umsg_' + Date.now());"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"id\": \"{{ultraMsgId}}\",\n  \"from\": \"593991234567@c.us\",\n  \"type\": \"chat\",\n  \"body\": \"Hola desde Postman vía UltraMsg\",\n  \"senderName\": \"Cliente UltraMsg\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/webhooks/{{tenantKey}}/whatsapp/{{whatsappChannelId}}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "03 — Integraciones (escalate)",
      "description": "Simula sistemas externos (bot, IVR, AgentHub). Requiere X-Tenant-Key + x-api-key.\nÚtil para WhatsApp, Webchat, Email, Teams, Voz sin configurar webhook del proveedor.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Escalate — WhatsApp",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "  const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (data.conversation_id) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('lastConversationId', data.conversation_id);",
                  "  }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Tenant-Key", "value": "{{tenantKey}}" },
              { "key": "x-api-key", "value": "{{integrationApiKey}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"source_system\": \"postman_bot\",\n  \"channel_type\": \"whatsapp\",\n  \"event_type\": \"escalation\",\n  \"conversation_ref_id\": \"postman-wa-{{$timestamp}}\",\n  \"escalation_reason\": \"Cliente solicita agente humano\",\n  \"preferred_queue\": \"General\",\n  \"priority\": 3,\n  \"contact\": {\n    \"phone\": \"+593991234567\",\n    \"name\": \"Cliente Postman WA\",\n    \"external_id\": \"postman-contact-wa\"\n  },\n  \"context\": {\n    \"last_message\": \"Necesito ayuda con mi pedido\",\n    \"simulated_from\": \"postman\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/integrations/escalate"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Escalate — Webchat",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "  const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (data.conversation_id) pm.collectionVariables.set('lastConversationId', data.conversation_id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Tenant-Key", "value": "{{tenantKey}}" },
              { "key": "x-api-key", "value": "{{integrationApiKey}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"source_system\": \"postman_webchat\",\n  \"channel_type\": \"webchat\",\n  \"event_type\": \"escalation\",\n  \"conversation_ref_id\": \"postman-wc-{{$timestamp}}\",\n  \"escalation_reason\": \"Visitante web pide asesor\",\n  \"contact\": {\n    \"name\": \"Visitante Web\",\n    \"external_id\": \"session-postman-001\"\n  },\n  \"context\": {\n    \"page_url\": \"https://ejemplo.com/soporte\",\n    \"message\": \"Hola, ¿hay alguien disponible?\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/integrations/escalate"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Escalate — Email",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Tenant-Key", "value": "{{tenantKey}}" },
              { "key": "x-api-key", "value": "{{integrationApiKey}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"source_system\": \"postman_mail\",\n  \"channel_type\": \"email\",\n  \"event_type\": \"escalation\",\n  \"conversation_ref_id\": \"postman-mail-{{$timestamp}}\",\n  \"contact\": {\n    \"email\": \"cliente@ejemplo.com\",\n    \"name\": \"Cliente Email\",\n    \"external_id\": \"postman-mail-001\"\n  },\n  \"context\": {\n    \"subject\": \"Consulta facturación\",\n    \"body\": \"Buenos días, necesito una copia de mi factura.\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/integrations/escalate"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Escalate — Voz (IVR)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Tenant-Key", "value": "{{tenantKey}}" },
              { "key": "x-api-key", "value": "{{integrationApiKey}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"source_system\": \"postman_ivr\",\n  \"channel_type\": \"voice\",\n  \"event_type\": \"escalation\",\n  \"conversation_ref_id\": \"postman-voice-{{$timestamp}}\",\n  \"escalation_reason\": \"IVR transfiere a cola general\",\n  \"preferred_queue\": \"General\",\n  \"contact\": {\n    \"phone\": \"+593991234567\",\n    \"name\": \"Llamante Postman\"\n  },\n  \"context\": {\n    \"ani\": \"+593991234567\",\n    \"dnis\": \"1800123456\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/integrations/escalate"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "04 — Bandeja manual (auth)",
      "description": "Crea conversaciones desde la API como agente autenticado. Ejecutar Login antes.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Crear conversación — Webchat",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "  const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (data.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('lastConversationId', data.id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{accessToken}}", "type": "string" }]
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Tenant-Key", "value": "{{tenantKey}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"channel_type\": \"webchat\",\n  \"queue_id\": \"General\",\n  \"subject\": \"Chat web simulado\",\n  \"contact\": {\n    \"name\": \"Visitante Manual\",\n    \"phone\": \"+593991234567\"\n  },\n  \"initial_message\": \"Conversación creada desde Postman para probar routing\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/conversations"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Crear conversación — WhatsApp",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{accessToken}}", "type": "string" }]
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Tenant-Key", "value": "{{tenantKey}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"channel_type\": \"whatsapp\",\n  \"queue_id\": \"General\",\n  \"contact\": {\n    \"name\": \"Cliente WA Manual\",\n    \"phone\": \"+593991234567\"\n  },\n  \"initial_message\": \"Seguimiento manual desde Postman\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/conversations"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "05 — Routing y consultas",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar conversaciones (tab queue)",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{accessToken}}", "type": "string" }]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "X-Tenant-Key", "value": "{{tenantKey}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/conversations?tab=queue&limit=50&page=1",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["conversations"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "tab", "value": "queue" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "50" },
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar conversaciones — filtro WhatsApp",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{accessToken}}", "type": "string" }]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "X-Tenant-Key", "value": "{{tenantKey}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/conversations?tab=queue&channel=WHATSAPP&limit=50",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["conversations"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "tab", "value": "queue" },
                { "key": "channel", "value": "WHATSAPP" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "50" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Disparar routing (auto)",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{accessToken}}", "type": "string" }]
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Tenant-Key", "value": "{{tenantKey}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"conversation_id\": \"{{lastConversationId}}\",\n  \"target_type\": \"auto\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/routing/assign"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Colas en vivo",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{accessToken}}", "type": "string" }]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "X-Tenant-Key", "value": "{{tenantKey}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/queues/live"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
